Package: rusty-wire
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Wire antenna length calculator for amateur radio operators
 rusty-wire calculates optimal wire antenna lengths for amateur radio use,
 taking into account frequency, velocity factor, and ITU/amateur band
 constraints. It ships both a non-interactive CLI mode and a full-screen
 terminal user interface (TUI).
